{"tid":382853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高鐵宣傳片收到237宗投訴誤導  「真實版」廣告吸34萬人次瀏覽","createTime":"2017-09-01T04:36:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-06T06:21:16.000Z","uid":79563,"like":159,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"6f6c411d771433828bb233b8711084082ac6db76","tid":382853,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T04:36:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w1HeLNl1KPM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dw1HeLNl1KPM&d=Iyc%2FzmFkNyrh6TxhnKm03ywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=e4dea95a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w1HeLNl1KPM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170901/large/1504198038_a978.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170901%2Flarge%2F1504198038_a978.png&h=c7c20907&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵新一輯高鐵宣傳片，過去多天在各大電視台熱播，惟片中聲稱日後由沙田去廣州，去西九站搭高鐵快過去羅湖站搭和諧號，出鏡的藝人黃心穎更在旁白聲言，搭高鐵「只須48分鐘車程，就直達廣州啦！」字幕卻不起眼地補充，只是「直達廣州（南）」，惹來不少人質疑屬誤導性遺漏，涉違反《商品說明條例》，誤導觀眾。通訊局截至昨午5時，共收到237宗投訴。<br />\n<br />\n新民主同盟區議員譚凱邦日前在facebook上載惡搞片段，還原真相，反駁搭高鐵去廣州，不止直達班次極少，而且車站根本不在市中心，若乘搭「站站停」的高鐵班次，加上轉乘廣州地鐵往天河區，根本慢過搭和諧號。此真實版「高鐵廣告」短短2日多，已吸引逾34萬人次瀏覽，逾8,000人讚好或感到好笑。"},{"pid":"05cf0537947e28f7cbdd205ce88e1b7748346f67","tid":382853,"uid":20815,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:02:28.000Z","msg":"其實一地兩檢都未落實，咁賣廣告法係咪會違反商品說明條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9007e1bf904af3fefbccd412762458ff6f3ae3ff","tid":382853,"uid":51720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:19:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實一地兩檢都未落實，咁賣廣告法係咪會違反商品說明條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔關一地兩檢事；而廣州市中心（中心商貿區），正正係珠江新城一帶。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n橫掂紅磡站改建重置月台後，原東鐵綫、西鐵綫月台，<br />\n或會改造成廣深線直通車專用月台（行 CRH1之類列車）。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7643d9bbac485064464fdd1cae87ceca8e8fed97","tid":382853,"uid":609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3383fcc30daebdaa88c5baebae1e695064ff979e","tid":382853,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:26:50.000Z","msg":"補充：上述個人意見純屬猜測，只係以鐵路公司既有工程公開資料作推測。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f742b8398e464f4e68ca6461a485c90b28ead1","tid":382853,"uid":46454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:27:40.000Z","msg":"廣州南站係番禺,搭返去天河區市中心要半個鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n深圳北都一樣,返黎羅湖福田都要半個鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d719793f5e58895d7d5df2273c5cf11c2f7642","tid":382853,"uid":19676,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:28:38.000Z","msg":"賓潁食屎"},{"pid":"5bdc98e6deac7b57353b7a605f04215edcf8a0ed","tid":382853,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:29:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706748b084dbc98998fe5ba22ad8aea625232aa6","tid":382853,"uid":51775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:30:53.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"559feff76392bcb03f36ebcebb50c810e8ff6cb0","tid":382853,"uid":5056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T05:31:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實一地兩檢都未落實，咁賣廣告法係咪會違反商品說明條例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔關一地兩檢事；而廣州市中心（中心商貿區），正正係珠江新城一帶。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgm